name: text_688
text:
A keyboard-centric drawing app with an infinite
 canvas. Inspired by Vim motions and Vimium

name: text_696
text:
- press      to move camera RIGHT
- press     to move the camera LEFT

name: text_706
text:
- press      to move camera DOWN
- press     to move the camera UP

name: text_709
text:
- press      to move camera to Zoom Out
- press     to Zoom In

name: text_717
text:
- press      to draw a rectangle
- press     to draw a circle
- press     to draw a line
- press     to draw text
- press     to draw a dashes line
- press     to draw an arrow
- press     to draw a triangle
- press     to draw a checkmark

text: Press the number keys before executing an action to modify its effect

- press           then      in scale mode to increase height by 30 pixels

name: text_863
text:
The fundamental principle behind Magnetic8 is the magnetic force that creates grouping between shapes. 
When shapes are magnetized with other shapes, they form cohesive groups while maintaing their individual properties

name: text_865
text: After selecting a shape, activate                               by pressing

name: text_866
text: - press      again to magnetize other shapes withour changing their position

name: text_867
text:
- use     ,     ,     ,      to attract other shapes using the magnetic force, the magnetized
shape will change the position to be near the parent shape

name: text_889
text:
Activated by pressing      , this mode enables quick 
selection of shapes
- each shape displays a keyboard hint 
- type the displayed hint to select the corresponding shape
- press       to cancel the selection

name: text_896
text: Transform the border of the selected shape

name: text_898
text:
- press      to enter shape border mode
- use     ,      to adjust the border roundness
- use     , a   to adjust the border width

name: text_909
text:
- press        +     to activate selection of magnetized 
children, as default only the magnetized parents can be
selected

name: text_914
text:
- press        to select the most recent created shapes
in reverse order

name: text_915
text:
- press        +         to select the most recent created
shapes in ascending order

name: text_924
text: Transform the color of the selected shape

name: text_926
text:
- press      to change the primary color
- use     ,   +      to change the secondary color

name: text_935
text: Transform the opacity of the selected shape color

name: text_937
text:
- press      to enter color opacity mode
- use     ,      to adjust primary color opacity
- use     , a   to adjust secondary color opacity

name: text_950
text:
- Note! some shapes have as default the primary
color with reduced opacity. 
Remember to increase it.

name: text_951
text:
- press        +        to activate selection of locked shape,
 Note! the hint will be visible only in the Shapes panel
form the right side of the screen
- press     to delete a selected shape
- press     to copy a shape or magnetized group,
press     to paste it. Note! the paste works only if a 
shape is selected

name: text_964
text: Give a name to your shapes

name: text_966
text: - press      to rename the selected shape
